{"tid":1299832,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：取消自娛區，無撚用！","createTime":"2019-07-09T07:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T16:40:24.000Z","uid":46804,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f64f3b2af94ce5cf47a6475d4dce6eb6d9269d31","tid":1299832,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:30:46.000Z","msg":"人話：屯門公園大媽唱歌係執法問題。未來大媽會在非自娛區唱歌會繼續<br />\n<br />\n鄭松泰：今日屯區區議會在沒有「反對」下，通過取消屯門公園自娛區的議案。<br />\n<br />\n一、大家要清楚這是區議會議案，還要交予康文署「決定」，未正式完成取消程序（當然，區議會的一致意見，康文署一般不會拒絕）；<br />\n<br />\n二、大媽（大陸）劣文化，始終令香港的公共空間及公共秩序攬炒。在正常社會，公園不能娛樂、不讓休憩是專制、是苛政；一直以來是康文署及政府執法偏頗/不力的問題；<br />\n<br />\n三、始終本土議題，緊密連結人民的日常生活，要令香港「優雅」、重塑內涵，唯有本土主張。<br />\n<br />\n**補充：<br />\n其實屯門公園絕大部分的色情大媽一般在自娛區外面唱歌，因為自娛區需要申請，且有條款限制。所以有沒有自娛區其實沒有解決問題，分別不大。<br />\n況且，康文署本身有權執法，但每次被要求執法時，職員往往推波給沒有執法權的保安員，只去度分貝，度完算數扮做嘢。"},{"pid":"59ea5a776662d94d98b771743de497beb545c4a5","tid":1299832,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23dce43f0dd76f29b30a408b6b6b350a35c7736","tid":1299832,"uid":46804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"59ea5a776662d94d98b771743de497beb545c4a5","tid":1299832,"uid":171643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:34:48.000Z","msg":"以為成功爭取，其實依然存在。公園涼亭，橋，單車徑上繼續和大叔跳舞"},{"pid":"c278c63b04fad1637b65e4aa22be0ca984a486c1","tid":1299832,"uid":15948,"like":31,"dislike":8,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰都唔見得幾撚有用"},{"pid":"37904ed11694587fb8fc99b61e3dc292642be5fe","tid":1299832,"uid":202730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:35:36.000Z","msg":"呢個又錯唔曬"},{"pid":"52e7b5ad81eb5ccc3f70f7ba4c8418243074678f","tid":1299832,"uid":41292,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"c278c63b04fad1637b65e4aa22be0ca984a486c1","tid":1299832,"uid":15948,"like":31,"dislike":8,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:35:26.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰都唔見得幾撚有用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"係囉，你呢？"},{"pid":"ec329536de394a892426027ffb27096c8dffad78","tid":1299832,"uid":46804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:37:40.000Z","msg":"核心問題，公安要保安報法。保安又被大媽保安搞。公安又唔理大媽保安。整個屯門公園跟本係大媽保安搞出自治地區"},{"pid":"8a11c4bb4516bf29fc2e2581fe9663c1c8b367f8","tid":1299832,"uid":46804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:38:23.000Z","msg":"核心問題公安要保安報法。保安又被大媽保安搞。公安又唔理大媽保安。整個屯門公園跟本係大媽保安搞出自治地區"},{"pid":"bfa9fcf4b337dd65ff98e3da1142ce41b91793c4","tid":1299832,"uid":46804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"屯門公園跟本係康文署失職"},{"pid":"3d2b4c28d327e9867847eafca55a7a1735ed0bcd","tid":1299832,"uid":263161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78235a9c9fc8ed77d74f67b2f1d844938f76e51f","tid":1299832,"uid":46804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:27:38.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"a44e15dc4762cbaa4ab731dc1d4e241d9cf72e84","tid":1299832,"uid":162906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl